sc4ve:ColorizeCommand        sc4ve:grounding "{n} objet(s) colorié(s)"@fr , "{n} object(s) colored"@en .
sc4ve:ColorizeLighterCommand sc4ve:grounding "{n} objet(s) éclairci(s)"@fr , "{n} object(s) lightened"@en .
sc4ve:ColorizeDarkerCommand  sc4ve:grounding "{n} objet(s) assombri(s)"@fr , "{n} object(s) darkened"@en .
