sc4ve:HideCommand            sc4ve:grounding "{n} objet(s) masqué(s)"@fr , "{n} object(s) hidden"@en .
sc4ve:ShowCommand            sc4ve:grounding "{n} objet(s) affiché(s)"@fr , "{n} object(s) shown"@en .
sc4ve:DeleteCommand          sc4ve:grounding "{n} objet(s) supprimé(s)"@fr , "{n} object(s) deleted"@en .
sc4ve:RotateLeftCommand      sc4ve:grounding "{n} objet(s) pivoté(s)"@fr , "{n} object(s) rotated"@en .
sc4ve:RotateRightCommand     sc4ve:grounding "{n} objet(s) pivoté(s)"@fr , "{n} object(s) rotated"@en .
