sc4ve:AlignCommand           sc4ve:grounding "{n} objet(s) aligné(s)"@fr , "{n} object(s) aligned"@en .
sc4ve:FocusCommand           sc4ve:grounding "Caméra centrée sur {n} objet(s)"@fr , "Camera focused on {n} object(s)"@en .
